<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1436,1736,2015]" pageId="8" pageNumber="110">
In North Africa, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Muller" authorityYear="1806" box="[383,491,1846,1871]" class="Insecta" family="Elmidae" genus="Limnius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="110" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="opacus">
<emphasis box="[383,491,1846,1871]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="110">L. opacus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is known only in 
<collectingCountry box="[688,789,1845,1871]" name="Morocco" pageId="8" pageNumber="110">Morocco</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[840,928,1845,1871]" name="Algeria" pageId="8" pageNumber="110">Algeria</collectingCountry>
. The previous Algerian records of this species are from Mouzaïa and the Djurdjura massifs (
<bibRefCitation author="Berthelemy, C." box="[663,861,1881,1907]" pageId="8" pageNumber="110" pagination="244 - 285" refId="ref8801" refString="Berthelemy, C. (1964) Elminthidae d'Europe occidentale et meridionale et d'Afrique du Nord (Coleopteres). Bulletin de la Societe d'Histoire Naturelle de Toulouse, 99 (1 - 2), 244 - 285." type="journal article" year="1964">Berthélemy 1964</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Lounaci, A." box="[873,1031,1881,1907]" pageId="8" pageNumber="110" refId="ref10605" refString="Lounaci, A. (1987) Recherches hydrobiologiques sur les peuplements d'invertebres benthiques du bassin de l'oued Aissi (Grande Kabylia). These de Magister. Universite des Sciences et de la technologie Houari Boumediene. Institut des sciences de la nature, Alger, 133 pp." type="book" year="1987">Lounaci 1987</bibRefCitation>
, 2005; 
<bibRefCitation author="Ait Mouloud, S." box="[1112,1323,1881,1907]" pageId="8" pageNumber="110" refId="ref8347" refString="Ait Mouloud, S. (1988) Essais de recherches sur la derive des macro-invertebres dans l'oued Aissi: faunistique, ecologie et biogeographie. These de Magister, Universite des Sciences et de la Technologie Houari Boumediene. Institut des Sciences de la Nature, d'Alger, Algerie, 118 pp." type="book" year="1988">Aït Mouloud 1988</bibRefCitation>
; Lounaci- Daoudi 1996). During the present study, it was captured in five additional locations at altitudes between 
<quantity box="[1318,1389,1917,1943]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.6" pageId="8" pageNumber="110" unit="m" value="160.0">160 m</quantity>
and 
<quantity box="[151,221,1953,1979]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.8" pageId="8" pageNumber="110" unit="m" value="380.0">380 m</quantity>
in habitats of middle-reach streams, with intermittent flow. Four out of the five sites are impacted by domestic water pollution and sand and gravel extraction.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1437,152,287]" pageId="9" pageNumber="111">
In 
<collectingCountry box="[229,333,153,179]" name="Morocco" pageId="9" pageNumber="111">Morocco</collectingCountry>
, although the species is recorded at altitudes between 
<quantity box="[933,989,153,179]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.0" pageId="9" pageNumber="111" unit="m" value="60.0">60 m</quantity>
and 
<quantity box="[1042,1129,152,179]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.5" pageId="9" pageNumber="111" unit="m" value="2500.0">2500 m</quantity>
, it is more abundant at high altitudes (
<bibRefCitation author="Bennas, N. &amp; Sainz-Cantero, C. E." box="[261,608,189,215]" pageId="9" pageNumber="111" pagination="61 - 79" refId="ref8596" refString="Bennas, N. &amp; Sainz-Cantero, C. E. (2007) Nouvelles donnees sur les Coleopteres aquatiques du Maroc: les Elmidae Curtis, 1830 et les Dryopidae Billberg, 1820 du Rif (Coleoptera). Nouvelle Revue d'Entomologie, 24 (1), 61 - 79." type="journal article" year="2007">Bennas &amp; Sáinz-Cantero 2007</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Benamar, L." box="[620,789,188,215]" pageId="9" pageNumber="111" refId="ref8555" refString="Benamar, L. (2015) Les Coleopteres aquatiques du Maroc: atlas, biogeographie et degre de vulnerabilite. These de Doctorat d'etat en Sciences, Universite Abdelmalek Essaadi, Faculte des Sciences, Tetouan, 538 pp." type="book" year="2015">Benamar 2015</bibRefCitation>
). In 
<collectingCountry box="[837,922,189,215]" name="Austria" pageId="9" pageNumber="111">Austria</collectingCountry>
, the species prefers warmer streams, approximately from the metarhithral to epipotamal zone (
<bibRefCitation author="Jach, M. A. &amp; Dietrich, F. &amp; Raunig, B." box="[714,899,224,251]" pageId="9" pageNumber="111" pagination="211 - 284" refId="ref10072" refString="Jach, M. A., Dietrich, F. &amp; Raunig, B. (2005) Rote Liste der Zwergwasserkafer (Hydraenidae) und Krallenkafer (Elmidae) Osterreichs (Insecta: Coleoptera). In: Zulka, P. (Ed.), Rote Listen gefahrdeter Tiere Osterreichs. Checklisten, Gefahrdungsanalyse, Handlungsbedarf. Part 1. Saugetiere, Vogel, Heuschrecken, Wasserkafer, Netzflugler, Schnabelfliegen, Tagfalter (Grune Reihe des Lebensministeriums. Vol. 14 / 1. Bundesministerium fur Land-und Forstwirtschaft, Umwelt und Wirtschaft, Wien, pp. 211 - 284." type="book chapter" year="2005">
Jäch 
<emphasis box="[774,831,225,251]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="111">et al.</emphasis>
2005
</bibRefCitation>
). In 
<collectingCountry box="[950,1043,225,251]" name="Czech Republic" pageId="9" pageNumber="111">Czechia</collectingCountry>
, the species was listed as critically endangered by 
<bibRefCitation author="Boukal, D. S." box="[322,487,260,287]" pageId="9" pageNumber="111" pagination="462 - 463" refId="ref8930" refString="Boukal, D. S. (2005) Elmidae. In: Farkac, J., Kral, D. &amp; Skorpik, M. (Eds.), Cerveny seznam ohrozenych druhu Ceske republiky. Bezobratli-Red list of threatened species in the Czech Republic. Agentura ochrany poirody a krajiny ER, Praha, pp. 462 - 463." type="book chapter" year="2005">Boukal (2005)</bibRefCitation>
, and later as regionally extinct (
<bibRefCitation author="Boukal, D. S. &amp; Boukal, M. &amp; Fikacek, M. &amp; Hajek, J. &amp; Klecka, J. &amp; Skalicky, S. &amp; Stastny, J. &amp; Travnicek, D." box="[845,1058,261,287]" pageId="9" pageNumber="111" pagination="1 - 289" refId="ref8994" refString="Boukal, D. S., Boukal, M., Fikacek, M., Hajek, J., Klecka, J., Skalicky, S. Stastny, J. &amp; Travnicek, D. (2007) Katalog vodnich brouku Ceske republiky-Catalogue of water beetles of the Czech Republic. Klapalekiana, 43 (Supplementum), 1 - 289." type="journal article" year="2007">
Boukal 
<emphasis box="[934,983,261,287]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="111">et al</emphasis>
. 2007
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
